==English==

===Noun===

'''jill'''

#A young woman; a sweetheart.
#any female, as in [[jillstrap]] (also shortened as jill), the female counterpart of a [[jockstrap]]

===Etymology===
a variant of the proper name [[Gill]], itself a female form either of [[Julius]] (then also Gillian) or of [[Aegidius]]

